This variable is a 'virtual' variable that is computed using the function alternate_view (see https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/pub/software/cdawlib/source/virtual_funcs.pro) on the with inputs of the variables ['mag_lat_foot']. Note that some COMPONENTS may not be available from the HAPI interface. They are accessible from the raw CDF files, however.
